name: DBDT TOKEN
description: DaddyBabyDoge is a Binance Smart Chain protocol, with reflections functions DaddyBabyDoge pays its holders rewards in the world famous coin BabyDoge. DaddyBabyDoge has as its main objective the creation of its own Play-To-Earn game that will be powered by the token itself in its economy. DaddyBabyDoge knows that publicity and marketing are very important points for a project to be really successful, so DaddyBabyDoge will seek the best partners in the market so that it reaches the world community with strength.
